                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.00/1083</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-02-14T23:00:00-05:29">
                            <hi rend="italic">February, 14, 1917—11 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Publication of statement giving position of United States regarding revolutions
                    has had most clarifying effect upon public mind and the Government officials
                    deeply grateful.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
